long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Dive into the fast-paced world of "Money Rush," the ultimate hypercasual game that will challenge your reflexes and strategic thinking! Get ready for an adrenaline-pumping experience as you embark on a thrilling journey to amass wealth and conquer the financial leaderboard.

🌟 **Features:**

💸 **Race Against Time:** Time is money, and in "Money Rush," every second counts! Can you make it to the finish line before the clock runs out?

🚀 **Speed and Precision:** Test your reflexes and agility as you control your character through a maze of challenges. Swipe, tap, and tilt your device to dodge obstacles and collect as much cash as possible. The faster and more precise you are, the richer you become!

Get ready to embark on the ultimate financial adventure in "Money Rush"! Can you navigate the obstacles, beat the clock, and become the wealthiest player in the hypercasual gaming universe? Start your Money Rush now and let the fortune chase begin!

HOW TO PLAY
You can move with the arrow keys, mouse  or W-A-S-D keys.

HOW TO INSTALL
Click download this Extension using the "Add to Chrome" button.

Once the game has finished loading, simply select the "Extensions Icon" button. 

After clicking this, you'll be directed to the playground area, where the game "Money Rush" will launch automatically. All that's left is to press the play button and start enjoying the game.
